                            <a href="#" class="flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 dark:hover:text-white"><svg class="mr-2 h-5 w-5 text-gray-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg> My likes</a>
